Package: meandr
Type: Package
Title: Easily generate continuous coordinates following random trajectory
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Author: Scott McKenzie <sccmckenzie@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Scott McKenzie <sccmckenzie@gmail.com>
Description: Generate random coordinates that are continuously differentiable.
    This is particularly useful for simulating time-series measurements of physical phenomena that maintain a clear local trajectory.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
